nhc_headline: ...TROPICAL STORM HUMBERTO FORMS IN CENTRAL TROPICAL ATLANTIC...
summary: ...TROPICAL STORM HUMBERTO FORMS IN CENTRAL TROPICAL ATLANTIC... As of 5:00 PM AST Wed Sep 24 the center of Humberto was located near 20.1, -54.9 with movement WNW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1008 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 40 mph.
